    "title": "defineBlock(): How I Built a Full-Stack Database Abstraction on Cloudflare Workers",
    "description": "I tried SpacetimeDB, wrote a blog post about it, then deleted it two days later. But the syntax stuck. Here's how I rebuilt those patterns on Cloudflare Workers and migrated my entire platform in a weekend.",
